dimension 2

Pb_conduction pb
Domaine dom



VDF dis

Scheme_euler_explicit sch
Read sch
{
	tinit 0
	tmax 300.
	dt_min 0.00001
	dt_max 0.1
	dt_impr 5
	dt_sauv 100
	seuil_statio 1.e-8
}

Solide sol
Read sol
{
	rho Champ_Uniforme 1 2
	lambda Champ_Uniforme 1 0.01
	Cp Champ_Uniforme 1 0.5
}

Associate pb dom
Associate pb sch
Associate pb sol

Discretize pb dis

Read pb
{
	Conduction
	{
		diffusion { }
		initial_conditions {
			temperature Champ_Uniforme 1 0. 
			}
		boundary_conditions {
			Haut paroi_adiabatique
			Bas paroi_temperature_imposee
			        Champ_Front_Uniforme 1 5.
			Droit paroi_adiabatique
			Gauche paroi_adiabatique
		}
	}
} /* Read pb */

Solve pb

End

